{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLCLightOnOffSetUnacknowledged"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLCLightOnOffSetUnacknowledged\/delay","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh34LightLCLightOnOffSetUnacknowledgedV5delays5UInt8VSgvp","title":"delay","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"synchronized."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file has to be set together with "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lightlclightonoffsetunacknowledged\/delay"]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightLCLightOnOffSetUnacknowledged/delay":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLCLightOnOffSetUnacknowledged\/delay","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lightlclightonoffsetunacknowledged\/delay","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"delay"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightLCLightOnOffSetUnacknowledged":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\